title: Ep. 748 - Popatlal's Never Ending Melancholy - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is at Jetha's house and asks to share his sorrow with Jetha's father. Popatlal tells him that he is not married and hence does not have a family. Jetha's father tells him that being married and having a family are two different things.

title: Ep. 749 - Popatlal Throws A Party  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal goes to Dr. Hathi's house and invites him and his wife for a party at 1:20 in the afternoon. Hathi tells him that he looks sick and then tells him that it was just a joke. Everyone gathers and discusses the party that is about to happen.

title: Ep. 750 - An Invitation Or A Threat? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the men of Gokuldham society decide to ditch Popatlal's party. While they are deciding this, Popatlal hears them and threatens them one by one to reveal their secrets. Does Popatlal invite or threaten them?

title: Ep. 751 - Catching The Culprit - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Mr. Chaalu Pandey and Jetha tie hands and decide to catch the culprit. They search everywhere in the mall, where the culprit is hiding and come up with few plans on how to catch him! Watch to find out!

title: Ep. 752 - Taarak's Got Jetha's Back - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Like a usual day, Jetha rants about his issues to Taarak and thanks to him for being his fire brigade and having his back. To which, Taarak gives him a reality check that it all comes with a price and he has to sacrifice something.

title: Ep. 753 - Reminiscing The Good Old Days - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baapu Ji shares his childhood days with Jetha and Daya, that good was his young days when they used to enjoy outside in nature and that there's nothing that is in comparison with the enjoyment that gave.

title: Ep. 754 - An Emergency In Gokuldham Society - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal was taking a walk in his balcony, only to see his rooftop almost collapsing on him, when few parts of the ceiling fall on him. He then rushes to call the rest of the society members and urges for immediate action to be taken.

title: Ep. 755 - Gokuldham Society To Be Renovated? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The renovators come and take a look at the society's condition and want to do a regular check-up of how strong the walls are, and hence make a decision whether or not the society will be renovated.

title: Ep. 756 - Will Jetha Get A Fine? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the members have decided to keep a society meeting in the night around 9 PM, and Jetha puts forth his reasonable point of view that what if he gets late, then what will happen? Watch to find out if he will have to pay the fine!

title: Ep. 757 - The Negotiation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The final decision comes out that the society needs a bit of reconstruction due to its old walls that won't seem to last long if they don't renovate it. Soon later, they negotiate on the plan!

title: Ep. 758 - Popatlal Annoys Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal is completely annoyed with Popatlal's suggestions. He comes back home with a sad face and does not know what to do. Will Champaklal and Daya help him sort this?

title: Ep. 759 - Construction In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka and Baga convince Jetha for a contract of the construction company. Jetha informs the same to Bhide and the others. In the end, Jetha gets a shocker. Can he overcome it?

title: Ep. 760 - Jetha Convinces Sundar - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As Jetha is shocked to see Sundar, he tries convincing others in not taking the contract. The society still wants to go ahead with the contract. Sundar also doesn't step back.

title: Ep. 761 - The Predictions - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha goes to Taarak to share his problems and ask for a solution. Meanwhile, they go to a saint to find answers. He says the future beholds more problems for Jetha.

title: Ep. 762 - Caught In The Act - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha tries playing around Sundar and gets out answers from him. Sundar, in turn, does the same. Later, while talking to Sundar, the truth surfaces.
